{"type":"click","text":"Option B\n    Layered — cinematic frame, professional core\n    \n      Homepage and transitions are cinematic (video, atmosphere, dramatic framing). Case studies and work pages stay clean and typographic. Two modes — the atmosphere is the frame, the work is the content inside it.\n    \n\n    / homepage — cinematic\n    \n      \n        \n        hkjstudio.com\n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n          \n            Brand film / ambient video loop\n          \n        \n        \n          hkj\n          Design Engineering · Ryan Jun\n        \n      \n    \n\n    / works — professional, warm\n    \n      \n        \n        hkjstudio.com/works\n      \n      \n        Work\n        \n          01\n          GYEOL · 결\n          MATERIAL · DIGITAL   2024\n        \n        \n          02\n          Conductor\n          DESIGN SYSTEM   WIP\n        \n        \n          03\n          Sift: Digital Sanctuary\n          MOBILE · AI   2025\n        \n        \n          04\n          Moji\n          DESIGN SYSTEMS   2025\n        \n        \n          05\n          하나 Hana\n          EDITORIAL · NUI   2025\n        \n      \n    \n\n    \n      The vibe: A cinematic overture that opens into a clean studio. The homepage is the emotional statement — video, atmosphere, mood. Then case studies are crisp, readable, trustworthy. You lead with feeling, then deliver substance. Two registers that complement each other.","choice":"layered","id":null,"timestamp":1773940617096}
{"type":"click","text":"Option A\n    Unified — one voice\n    \n      The cinematic atmosphere IS the portfolio. Cool palette everywhere. Every page carries the atmospheric quality. Case studies open with cinematic scenes. The professional and personal are inseparable.\n    \n\n    / homepage\n    \n      \n        \n        hkjstudio.com\n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n          hkj\n          /eɪtʃ-keɪ-dʒeɪ/\n          a quiet observer drawn to the space between craft and feeling; someone who builds things that breathe.\n        \n      \n    \n\n    / works\n    \n      \n        \n        hkjstudio.com/works\n      \n      \n        \n        \n          01\n          GYEOL · 결\n          MATERIAL · DIGITAL   2024\n        \n        \n          02\n          Conductor\n          DESIGN SYSTEM   WIP\n        \n        \n          03\n          Sift: Digital Sanctuary\n          MOBILE · AI   2025\n        \n        \n          04\n          Moji\n          DESIGN SYSTEMS   2025\n        \n        \n          05\n          하나 Hana\n          EDITORIAL · NUI   2025\n        \n      \n    \n\n    \n      The vibe: Walking through a quiet, atmospheric world. Every page has the same cool, moody treatment. Projects emerge from the fog. The music/cinematography sensibility is baked into every pixel. Visitors feel the aesthetic before they read a word.","choice":"unified","id":null,"timestamp":1773940618176}
{"type":"click","text":"Option B\n    Layered — cinematic frame, professional core\n    \n      Homepage and transitions are cinematic (video, atmosphere, dramatic framing). Case studies and work pages stay clean and typographic. Two modes — the atmosphere is the frame, the work is the content inside it.\n    \n\n    / homepage — cinematic\n    \n      \n        \n        hkjstudio.com\n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n          \n            Brand film / ambient video loop\n          \n        \n        \n          hkj\n          Design Engineering · Ryan Jun\n        \n      \n    \n\n    / works — professional, warm\n    \n      \n        \n        hkjstudio.com/works\n      \n      \n        Work\n        \n          01\n          GYEOL · 결\n          MATERIAL · DIGITAL   2024\n        \n        \n          02\n          Conductor\n          DESIGN SYSTEM   WIP\n        \n        \n          03\n          Sift: Digital Sanctuary\n          MOBILE · AI   2025\n        \n        \n          04\n          Moji\n          DESIGN SYSTEMS   2025\n        \n        \n          05\n          하나 Hana\n          EDITORIAL · NUI   2025\n        \n      \n    \n\n    \n      The vibe: A cinematic overture that opens into a clean studio. The homepage is the emotional statement — video, atmosphere, mood. Then case studies are crisp, readable, trustworthy. You lead with feeling, then deliver substance. Two registers that complement each other.","choice":"layered","id":null,"timestamp":1773940618791}
